headline: Zebra, ManpowerGroup, Magnite, Fair Isaac Corporation, and Hewlett Packard Enterprise Stocks Trade Down, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the morning session after the Trump administration's announcement of new global tariffs, reignited trade policy uncertainty.
